            "title": "戴爾盤前股價大漲；Gap與Firefly Aerospace下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YEgh6viO1EeINV4YtV0uxw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEBA90UC_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週五，美國股指期貨小幅上漲，受到美國與伊朗達成協議、延長停火並解除霍爾木茲海峽船隻通行限制的消息提振。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國東部時間上午6:55（北京時間18:55），道瓊斯期貨上漲101點，漲幅0.2%；標普500期貨上漲9點，漲幅0.1%；納斯達克100期貨上漲33點，漲幅0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下為今日美股盤前主要個股動態：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">戴爾股價大幅飆升，此前這家個人電腦製造商上調了全年獲利及營收展望，帶動同業超微電腦（Super Micro Computer）及慧與科技（Hewlett Packard Enterprise）股價同步大漲。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Gap股價下挫，原因是這家零售服裝連鎖商大幅下調了全年銷售預測。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">好市多（Costco）股價小幅下滑，儘管第三季銷售額優於市場預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香精香料製造商國際香料香精公司（International Flavors &amp; Fragrances）股價上漲，有報導指出該公司正接近達成協議，擬以逾40億美元將其食品原料部門出售給私募股權機構CVC Capital Partners。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Okta股價攀升，這家數位身份驗證公司公布的第一季營收超出市場預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Firefly Aerospace股價下跌逾3%，此前該公司宣布進行規模5.76億美元的股票發行計劃。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Agios製藥（Agios Pharmaceuticals）股價走低，這家罕見疾病治療藥物製造商在一項中期臨床試驗未能顯示足夠療效後，宣布終止其血液疾病藥物研發計劃。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>（路透社對本文亦有貢獻）</em></p></div>",
